*   [Thai](/Thai_language)
*   [Vietnamese](/Vietnamese_language)

This extensive list demonstrates [Naver](/Naver_Corporation)'s commitment to broad global coverage, attempting to cater to a significant portion of the world's internet users. One might even call it an admirable effort, if one were prone to such sentimentality.

